Cell[TextData[{
 "where the second-quantization operators are in the interaction picture, \
although the \[OpenCurlyQuote]I\[CloseCurlyQuote] superscript has been \
dropped. The single-particle indices in the expressions for ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["\[CapitalPi]", "acdb"], 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["g", "1"], 
